                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18740407-308-offence-1 t18740407-name-436"></join>Michael Burke</persName>, and stealing therein a coat, watch, and 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 1 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Second Count</hi>—feloniously receiving the same.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. FRITH</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">conducted the Prosecution.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18740407-name-437" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18740407-name-437" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18740407-name-437" type="surname" value="BURKE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18740407-name-437" type="given" value="MICHAEL"></interp>MICHAEL BURKE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at No. 20, George Street, Croome's Hill, Green wich—on the night of the 23rd February, I went to bed at 11.15, having secured my house—next morning I found the top sash of the front kitchen window had been shot down, and this over-coat and metal watch of mine were gone.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18740407-name-438" type="witnessName">
