                        <interp inst="t18740407-name-438" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH WOOLFORD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am married and live at No. 5, Benlaw Street—the prisoner asked me on Tuesday about six or seven weeks ago to pawn a watch for him—I did so, in the name of Davis—and he gave me 5 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18740407-name-439" type="witnessName">
