                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Phillips, Pawnbroker, Wellington Street, Deptford—the watch was pawned at our shop on the 24th February, for 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., in the name of Hannah Davis—I saw the prisoner at the time it was pawned.</p>
               <p>
